oku\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"58\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"3\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Full Array\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(84,'65\" Class LED UHD NU6950 4K Smart TV','With the clarity of the Samsung UN50NU6950FXZ50\" Class LED UHD NU6950 4K Smart TV get 4X the resolution of Full HD, plus non-4K TV content is upscaled to 4K via a powerful UHD engine. This TV is a clear upgrade for your content. With PurColor enjoy millions of shades of color, fine tuned to create an incredibly vibrant picture.','UN65NU6950FXZ','UN65NU6950FXZ',69,NULL,'products/img-0839--a54e7cd2555028cf7ebf38fa54fbbd45.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"65\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"2\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(85,'Samsung - 85\" Class Q80B QLED 4K UHD Smart Tizen TV','Don\'t settle for basic. Punch up the contrast with super-precise LEDs and elevate the ordinary to something more impressive. Direct Full Array and Dolby Atmos technology headline Samsung QLED\'s refined audio/visual experience','QN85Q80BAFXZA','653-6327',69,NULL,'products/img-0840--8c03f4d8b96fc52b6c716936493180f4.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"65\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(86,'Samsung - 75\" Class QN85CA Neo QLED 4K UHD Smart Tizen TV','Samsung Neo QLED 4K is a whole different deal. We\'re talking over a billion shades of color. Larger than life sound that reacts to the action on screen. And resolution that\'s automatically enhanced, no matter what you\'re watching.','QN75QN85CAFXZA','653-6416',69,NULL,'products/img-0842--aca07b85104e900a39517e83023c299c.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"75\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"2\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(87,'LG - 75\" Class 80 Series QNED 4K UHD Smart webOS TV','LG QNED80 combines cutting-edge Quantum Dots with LG\'s NanoCell technology to create uniquely bright, colorful images. The Al-powered LG QNED80 has a super-fast native 120Hz refresh rate, so you see smoother action; plus,\nDimming Pro dynamically adjusts the back lights to maintain deep black levels, allowing you to be fully immersed in your content. You\'ll enjoy outstanding picture powered by the a7\nAl Processor Gen6, which uses Al to detect what you\'re watching and automatically improves the picture and sound quality. You\'ll also experience less searching and more streaming, thanks to the next generation of Al technology from LG webOS 23. With Quick Cards, group your favorite apps into categories and use the Magic Remote to easily find what you\'re looking for—like instant access to over 300 free channels with LG Channels.\' Every moment will be enhanceo with virtual 5.1 surround sound for an immersive home theater experience. And transport yourself to the center of superhero-sized action and galaxies far, far','75QNED8OURA','6535920',70,NULL,'products/img-0844--5e0a0d9bd541eedc115983f1ef5ff66f.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"WebOS\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"75\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"2\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-