.1,15\nGet high-quality 4K UHD movies on us with the BRAVIA CORE™ app.2\nGame Menu puts all your gaming picture settings and exclusive assist features in one place.\nGet the advantage in high-performance gaming with HDMI 2.1 features like 4K/120, VRR, and ALLM.5\nTake your PlayStation® 5 gaming to the next level with exclusive features that optimize picture quality for gaming and streaming.\nEnjoy engaging cinematic content the way the creators intended with support for Dolby Vision®, IMAX® Enhanced, Netflix Adaptive Calibrated Mode, and more.8,9,','X93L','5649587658',71,NULL,'products/image--cab4b3dc9521d8de1cc1c249d36504a4.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"4\",\"system\":\"Google\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"65\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(279,'Sony BRAVIA XR 65” Class X93L Mini LED 4K HDR Google TV','Game Menu puts all your gaming picture settings and exclusive assist features in one place.\nGet the advantage in high-performance gaming with HDMI 2.1 features like 4K/120, VRR, and ALLM.5\nTake your PlayStation® 5 gaming to the next level with exclusive features that optimize picture quality for gaming and streaming.\nEnjoy engaging cinematic content the way the creators intended with support for Dolby Vision®, IMAX® Enhanced, Netflix Adaptive Calibrated Mode, and more.8,9,10\nWith Acoustic Multi-Audio™ and support for Dolby Atmos®, sound positioning tweeters produce wider, elevated sound that matches the picture you see.8\nAcoustic Center Sync synchronizes the TV speakers with select Sony soundbars, reinforcing the center speaker channel for clearer, fuller dialogue and more immersive sound.11\nBring back lost texture and detail and see all your HD content upscaled to near-4K resolution with XR 4K Upscaling.12\nSee blur-free picture quality in fast-