Dry - White','No one said laundry day was easy - but LG dryer innovations might just change your mind. It starts with the LG Sensor Dry system that measures the amount of moisture levels throughout the cycle and automatically adjusts the drying time. All the more reason to take advantage of the 7.3 cu. ft. extra large capacity that handles really large loads. You\'ll save time and energy.','DLE7000W','6450829',70,NULL,'products/img-0093--d195a3bf2603f7a28c43d05642fa47e0.jpeg',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,23,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/lg-7-3-cu-ft-electric-dryer-with-sensor-dry-white/JJ8VPZS8Q2'),(308,'Samsung - 6.0 cu. ft. Freestanding Gas Range with WiFi and Integrated Griddle - Stainless Steel','Elevate the look of your kitchen with Samsung’s Smart Freestanding Gas Range. Upgraded technology makes cooking with your stove simple and fun.','NX60A6111SS','6447914',69,NULL,'products/img-0094--d2f14b11fcce7fa17c4d5d2925d38acd.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,25,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/samsung-6-0-cu-ft-freestanding-gas-range-with-wifi-and-integrated-griddle-stainless-steel/J3ZYGC4Q87'),(309,'Samsung - 7.5 Cu. Ft. Stackable Gas Dryer with Sensor Dry - Black Stainless Steel','Samsung’s dryers have advanced features like Sensor Dry, which optimizes cycle time and temperature to thoroughly dry without damaging your clothes. Also, with 7.5 cu. ft. capacity and 10 preset drying cycles, you can do fewer loads in less time and fulfill almost every drying need.','DVG45T6000V','6427883',69,NULL,'products/img-0095--0027c1daddf0a080690970e3aa3db844.jpeg',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,23,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/samsung-7-5-cu-ft-stackable-gas-dryer-with-sensor-dry-black-stainless-steel/J3ZYGCT2CJ'),(310,'Samsung - 4.5 Cu. Ft. High Efficiency Stackable Smart Front Load Washer with Vibration Reduction Technology+ - White','Samsung’s Energy Star Certified Front Load washer has 4.5 cu. ft. capacity to fit more in every load and cut down on laundry time. It is equipped with Vibration Reduction Technology+ to reduce noise for quiet washing and features Self Clean+ to eliminate 99% of bacteria that can form in the drum.1','WF45T6000AW','6416171',69,NULL,'products/img-0096--6ffb2eebcfcaca27f803c14cc5728ed3.jpeg',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,22,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/samsung-4-5-cu-ft-high-efficiency-stackable-smart-front-load-washer-with-vibration-reduction-technology-white/J3ZYGCR8HK'),(311,'Samsung - Washer/Dryer Laundry Pedestal with Storage Drawer - Brushed Black','Compatible with Samsung 27\" front-load washers and dryers\nFor wide-ranging compatibility.','WE402NV/A3','11620107',69,NULL,'products/img-0098--ba0e7abf20123389f6ac42b79d49501b.jpeg',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,26,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/samsung-washer-dryer-laundry-pedestal-with-storage-drawer-brushed-black/J3ZYGCL43Z/sku/11620107?ref=212&loc=marketplace'),(312,'Vizio - 70” V-Series Class 4K UHD LED HDR Smart TV (V4K70M-08)','RETAIL WALMART $398','V4K70M-08','V4K70M-08',72,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"1\",\"system\":\"SmartCast\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"70\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"3\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Direct Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,'https://www.walmart.com/ip/VIZIO-70-Class-4K-UHD-LED-HDR-Smart-TV-New-V4K70M-08/5197667453'),(313,'Full Motion TV Wall Mount','Full Motion','SM-720-8904','SM-720-8904',82,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,10,'[]',1,'',NULL,''),(314,'Café - 22.3 Cu. Ft. 4-Door French Door Counter-Depth Smart Refrigerator, Customizable - Stainless Steel','RETAIL $4,299.99','CXE22DP2PS1','CXE22DP2PS1',88,NULL,'products/img-0099--6f9764dd7db1161ae9e8d8ad83fc48be.webp',NULL,NULL,8,NULL,27,'[]',2,'',NULL,'https://www.bestbuy.com/product/cafe-22-3-cu-ft-4-door-french-door-counter-depth-smart-refrigerator-customizable-stainless-steel/J7645S2WLT'),(315,