lity by restoring lost textures and improves low-quality content by reducing noise and enhancing details.','K65XR50','5838495',71,NULL,'products/image--82183e76e549d4e54f518b8125d6eef8.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Google\",\"screen-technology\":\"Qled\",\"screen-size\":\"65\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(361,'LG - 50” Class UA77 Series LED AI 4K UHD Smart webOS TV','4K UHD TV\nEverything you need to bring your favorite content to life with the power of 4K and the extras you crave.\n\nAlpha 7 AI Processor Gen8\nEnhanced brightness, improved sound, refined picture detail with 4K upscaling* and dynamic tone mapping. It all comes together for a thrilling watching experience powered by the Alpha 7 AI Processor Gen8.\n\nWebOS\nNo matter which TV you choose, your LG TV makes it easier than ever to find what you need and more. Browse all your favorite streaming apps and more.⁸','50UA7700PUB','78646576',70,NULL,'products/screenshot-2024-07-19-at-12-17-52-pm--97b58a6c1791df0f07e833b31c959ee6.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"3\",\"system\":\"WebOS\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"50\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Direct Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(362,'Samsung - 50” Class U8000F Series Crystal UHD 4K Smart Tizen TV','Crystal Processor 4K\nImmerse yourself in colorful, lifelike entertainment and catch every shade of color as it was meant to be seen in dazzling 4K resolution. Plus, enhance the clarity of your content with powerful 4K upscaling, ensuring that everything you watch—movies, TV shows, games and sports—looks sharp and clear, bringing every detail to life.\n\nMetalStream Design\nEnhance the look of your space with a sleek TV made from a single sheet of metal. Inspired by aircraft design, it showcases clean lines that beautifully balance form and function. With a slim bezel and elegant look, this TV not only enhances your décor but also minimizes distractions and expands your viewing.','UN50U8000FFXZA','675687678',69,NULL,'products/tempimagevolruw-02fe8a46a827d3c7a7dad2ef5fdfab44.png',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"50\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(363,'LG - 55” Class UA77 Series LED AI 4K UHD Smart webOS TV','4K UHD TV\nEverything you need to bring your favorite content to life with the power of 4K and the extras you crave.\n\nAlpha 7 AI Processor Gen8\nEnhanced brightness, improved sound, refined picture detail with 4K upscaling* and dynamic tone mapping. It all comes together for a thrilling watching experience powered by the Alpha 7 AI Processor Gen8.\n\nWebOS\nNo matter which TV you choose, your LG TV makes it easier than ever to find what you need and more. Browse all your favorite streaming apps and more.⁸','55UA7700PUB','6657687',70,NULL,'products/screenshot-2024-10-09-at-2-55-06-pm--9e74b619a3acfccb9a3da50d264ff66d.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"WebOS\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"55\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"2\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(364,'Samsung - 75” Class QN80F Series Neo QLED Mini LED 4K UHD SamsungVision AI Smart Tizen TV','Experience the power of AI¹ in your 4K TV. Powered by 20 neural networks, it makes all the movies, TV shows, video games and sports and you love to watch even better, by upscaling them to impressively beautiful 4K, even if the source content is lower resolution. The processor also optimizes sound, so no matter what you watch, you\'ll get a superb overall viewing experience.','QN75QN80FAFXZA','785767689',69,NULL,'products/image--ce5d294cf7ed435dd7be11f31723c72e.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"3\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Neo Qled\",\"screen-size\":\"75\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(365,'Samsung - 85\" Class U7900 Series UHD 4K Smart Tizen TV','Upgrade your home theater with this stylish 4K TV featuring vibrant colors, rich contrast and an advanced 4K processor. Stay endlessly entertained with thousands of on demand shows and movies for free and enjoy peace of mind as watch thanks to our proprietary triple layer security that protects your personal data across all connected devices at once.','UN85U7900FFXZA','6639193',69,NULL,'products/tempimage2o6dbz-02fe8a46a827d3c7a7dad2ef5fdfab44.png',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"85\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"3\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(366,'Samsung - 98” Class DU9000 Series Crystal UHD Smart Tizen TV','Make the most of your big screen with a wide picture ratio that displays every color in crisp 4K resolution. Add ultra smooth action and improved contrast to the mix for a hugely impressive view.','UN98DU9000FXZA','6578071',69,NULL,'products/tempimageika5ed-02fe8a46a827d3c7a7dad2ef5fdfab44.png',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"3\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"98\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"3\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(367,'Hisense - 100\" Class U8 Series MiniLED QLED UHD 4K HDR Smart Google TV','The Hisense U8 Series is an award-winning TV that makes for the ultimate game-watching experience. It’s enhanced with Mini-LED Pro technology, reaching up to 5,000 nits peak brightness for even sharper contrasts, brighter lighting and more dramatic shadows. Soak up over a billion vibrant shades on your screen with QLED Color. The 165Hz Native Refresh Rate and Anti-Glare Low Reflection Pro panel technology helps you see it all clearly without any interference. And Dolby Atmos','100U8QG','6621198',73,NULL,'products/image--be8d1e7286a62b156b4666ba48e899c2.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"4\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"100\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(368,'TCL - 115\" QM7K Series 4K UHD QD Mini LED Smart TV with Google TV','TCL QM7K Series Smart TVs offers the perfect TV for fast action movies, sports, and next level gaming TCL’s Halo Control System that includes the New Super High Energy LED Microchip, Condensed Micro Lens, Micro OD Reduced Optical Distance, CrystGlow HVA Panel, Enhanced QLED, Zero Delay Transient Response, Bi-direction 23-bit Backlight Controller, and Dynamic Light Algorithm for Stunning “Halo-Free” Images. With Up to LD2500 Precise Dimming Series and HDR 3000 nits peak brightness, you’ll experience pure black levels and a great picture in virtually any room lighting environment. TCL\'s AIPQ PRO Processor, an advanced processor optimizing each scene with machine learning provides an unrivaled cinematic experience. 144Hz native panel refresh rate with Motion Rate 480 focuses on best-in-class motion clarity producing smooth video playback. With TCL\'s Game Accelerator 240 and Auto Game Mode gameplay is blistering fast keeping you ahead of the competition.  The TCL 115QM7K features a 4.2.2 ONKYO speaker system as w','115QM7K','6621473',76,NULL,'products/85q651g-front-6c5726b742d4deb1ca2d3891b7fde4e9.png,products/50-65s451-nfl-front-079bb3051163a359635ff79effe1f5d7.png',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"4\",\"system\":\"Google\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"115\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"144Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"2\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(369,'TCL 85\" Q CLASS 4K QLED HDR SMART TV WITH GOOGLE TV - 85Q750G','Imagine everything you want in a TV including 120Hz Panel Refresh Rate, Full Array PRO Local Dimming, High Brightness PRO LED Backlight, the advanced TCL AIPQ Engine Gen3, Dolby Vision IQ, Game Accelerator 240 with AMD FreeSync Premium Pro Certification, IMAX Enhanced Certification, Hands Free Voice Control, Backlit Remote, and Adjustable Width Stand','85Q750G-CA','8465768775',76,NULL,'products/tempimageg0s5cz-a2713eae07e66e61b8fd50c992dd87fa.png',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"3\",\"system\":\"Google\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"85\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(370,'Roku - 75\" Class Pro Series 4K QLED Mini-LED Smart RokuTV','Elevate your entertainment. Roku Pro Series TVs bring you everything you love about Roku on an elevated canvas. Dazzling 4K picture on this flat screen smart TV immerses you in quantum dot color and brilliant contrast. Picture and audio automatically adjust to enhance your entertainment. Turn your living room into a theater with enveloping sound and a modern design that lets your flat screen TV rest flat against the wall. And of course, enjoy the powerfully simple home screen and fast access','75R8C5','86546576',81,NULL,'products/image-1--23248ebd45b441783666cb944882b271.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"3\",\"system\":\"Roku\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"75\",\"resolution\":\"4K UHD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"120Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(371,'75” Class Q6F Series QLED 4K UHD Samsung Vision AI Smart Tizen TV','Endlessly stream your favorite content in stunning clarity with a smart processor that upscales movies and shows regardless of source resolution. With dazzling, boosted color plus deep blacks & vibrant brights, previously hidden details are revealed in the brightest and darkest of scenes. Kick back, relax and see your favorite content in a whole new light.','QN75Q6FAAFXZA','6564565768',69,NULL,'products/image--5837fae9cc1a64c0acdf0198da57bc9c.jpeg',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,8,'{\"wifi\":\"1\",\"usb-ports\":\"2\",\"system\":\"Tyzen\",\"screen-technology\":\"Led-LCD\",\"screen-size\":\"75\",\"resolution\":\"HD\",\"refresh-rate\":\"60Hz\",\"high-dynamic-range-hdr\":\"1\",\"hdmi-ports-2-1\":\"0\",\"hdmi-ports\":\"4\",\"ethernet\":\"1\",\"back-light-type\":\"Edge Lit\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(372,'PG 12K BTU INVERTER LUXURY SEER2','PG INVERTER 12KBTU LUXURY','PG12KBTU','4823726482',86,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,20,'{\"btu\":\"12000\"}',2,'',NULL,''),(373,'PG 18K BTU SMART WIFI CONVENTIONAL','PG 18KBTU CONVENTIONAL SMART','727458747','5394875',86,NULL,'',NULL,NULL,2,NULL,20,'{\"btu\":\"18000\"}',2,'',NULL,'');
